Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your go-to bowling alley for fun and excitement. My name is Alex, and I will be assisting you today. May I know your name, please?

Hi Alex, my name is Jamie.

Nice to meet you, Jamie! How can I help you today?

I'm calling about a billing issue. I think I was overcharged for my last visit.

I'm sorry to hear that, Jamie. Let me help you look into it. Could you please provide me with your booking reference number?

Sure, it's two five six seven eight nine.

Thank you, Jamie. Could you also confirm the date of your visit?

Yes, it was on October fifteenth.

Great, let me check our records... Thank you for your patience, Jamie. It appears there was a mistake. I will process a refund for the extra charges promptly.

Thank you so much, Alex! I appreciate your help.

You're very welcome, Jamie. I appreciate your understanding. If there's anything else I can assist you with, feel free to reach out. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, and have a fantastic day!
